title: ANIGENE Surface Disinfectant Cleaner (5L – Unscented) - Disinfectant Solution For Use Around Animals & Pets, Kills Bacteria, Viruses, Fungi & Yeast – Non-Corrosive In Use - Made In The UK
features: ANIGENE Professional Disinfectant Liquid - The ideal solution to clean and disinfect surfaces used for pet and animal care like cat litter trays, crates, food and water bowls, hutches, and other hard surfaces. Our Liquid Concentrate kills germs fast

Effective Against Pet-specific Germs - Our professional strength formula is trusted by vets and designed to help you keep people and pets safe. ANIGENE provides effective cleansing and disinfection of Bacteria, Viruses, Yeast, and Fungi

500 Litres of Solution From Just 1 Bottle - Our sanitiser solution for pet and animal care offers vet quality disinfectant at brilliant value. With 1% dilution for general surface cleansing, you can make 500 litres of surface spray from one 5l bottle
Non-Corrosive, Liquid For Multi-Purpose Animal Surface Disinfection - In addition to being a brilliant cleaner, ANIGENE is also a powerful disinfectant which is non-corrosive in use

Made In The UK by Veterinary Environment and Animal Cleaning Experts - ANIGENE is powered by Byotrol. We have years of experience manufacturing quality industrial floor and surface cleaners & disinfectants to help keep you & your pets safe from germs
description: Product Description ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner ANIGENE provides the ultimate protection for veterinary practices and other professional animal environments, such as kennels, catteries, breeders, groomers and pet day care facilities. Its innovative cleaning technology kills harmful bacteria and viruses, without the use of bleach, ammonia, or phenols, which can harm pets and animals. Available in a range of fragrances as well as unfragranced, to suit all animal health environments. Always use ANIGENE Unfragranced in reptile or exotic animal environments. When using ANIGENE to disinfect water/food bowls and toys, please rinse off after use. Includes: PLEASE SELECT CORRECT OPTION FOR PRODUCT 2 x 5 Litre bottles of ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner concentrate - Lavender fragrance. 2 x 5 Litre bottles of ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner concentrate - Dill fragrance. 2 x 5 Litre bottles of ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner concentrate - Apple fragrance. 2 x 5 Litre bottles of ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner concentrate - Citrus fragrance. 2 x 5 Litre bottles of ANIGENE Professional Surface Disinfectant Cleaner concentrate - Unfragranced. Why disinfect? Disinfecting animal habitats and veterinary settings are essential for reducing the spread of diseases, and protecting animals and humans from infection. Disinfectant products are used to rid surfaces and items of bacteria, viruses, fungi, and other microscopic organisms that could put animal health at risk. Regular use of disinfectants in professional or home settings can help keep our animal companions safe and healthy by drastically reducing the risk of infection and cross-contamination. Furthermore, custodial staff members in veterinary settings must use a disinfectant which has been tested to veterinary protocols, to ensure it is suitable for animal environments. Cleaning and disinfecting cages, kennels, operating theatres and other areas that may come into contact with animals undergoing medical care, is essential to ensure all pathogens are removed Ingredients Didecyldimethylammonium Chloride 17.48g/kg, Alkyl (C12-16) Dimethylbenzyl Ammonium Chloride 17.48g/kg, N-(3-Aminopropyl)-N-dodecylpropane-1, 3-diamine 14.99g/kg. Contains Hexyl Cinnamal
